ggsegGordon 2.0.0
  • Reference

Gordon Resting-State Cortical Parcellation

Source: R/data.R
gordon.Rd

Brain atlas for the Gordon cortical parcellation with 329 regions based on resting-state functional connectivity boundaries. Contains 2D polygon geometry for ggseg::geom_brain().

gordon()

Value

A ggseg.formats::ggseg_atlas object (cortical).

References

Gordon EM, Laumann TO, Adeyemo B, Huckins JF, Kelley WM, Petersen SE (2016). Generation and Evaluation of a Cortical Area Parcellation from Resting-State Correlations. Cerebral Cortex, 26(1):288-303. doi:10.1093/cercor/bhu239
